The '''Kessilian hair knot''' was a hair style sported only in the [[Kessil system]]. [[Annikin Starkiller]] had one when he arrived on [[Aquilae (The Star Wars)|Aquilae]].

==Behind the scenes==
It is probable that this is the conceptual origin of the [[Padawan braid/Legends|Padawan braid]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|Episode I]] and [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|Episode II]], worn by [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]].

